{
  "content": [
	{"type": "sound", "sound_type": "bgm", "file_path": "BgmTest0"},
	{"type": "talk", "is_center": "1", "talk_content": "（窗外细雨绵绵，咖啡店的暖光洒在木桌上。）"},
	{"type": "background", "file_path": "BgTest0", "wait_tween_end": "1"},
	{"type": "talk", "talker": "小夜", "talk_content": "你来了啊。坐吧，我要跟你讲一件很重要的事。"},
	{"type": "tachie", "tachies": {"saya": {"file_path": "TachiTest0", "type": "show", "slot": "Center"}}},
	{"type": "talk", "talker": "小夜", "talk_content": "这件事我不能跟别人说……只能告诉你。"},
	{"type": "talk", "is_center": "1", "talk_content": "（她的表情变得严肃起来，轻轻握紧了杯子。）"},
	{"type": "tachie", "tachies": {"saya": {"file_path": "TachiTest0", "type": "change"}}},
	{"type": "talk", "talker": "小夜", "talk_content": "其实，这家咖啡店的老板……不是人类。"},
	{"type": "event", "event_name": "revelation_moment"},
	{"type": "talk", "talker": "我", "talk_content": "啊？你说什么？"},
	{"type": "talk", "talker": "小夜", "talk_content": "我亲眼看见过。那天深夜，他从后门进来，身后拖着一条……发光的尾巴。"},
	{"type": "tachie", "tachies": {"saya": {"type": "close"}}},
	{"type": "talk", "is_center": "1", "talk_content": "（沉默了几秒。雨声变得格外清晰。）"},
	{"type": "talk", "talker": "我", "talk_content": "你确定没看错？"},
	{"type": "talk", "talker": "小夜", "talk_content": "百分之百确定。而且……他似乎在找我。"},
	{"type": "talk", "talker": "小夜", "talk_content": "所以我现在需要你帮我——你愿意吗？"},
	{"type": "branch", "options": {
	  "help": {"text": "当然，我会帮你的。"},
	  "doubt": {"text": "你先冷静一下……这可能只是误会。"},
	  "leave": {"text": "转身离开", "wait": "1.5"}
	}},
	{"type": "talk", "talk_content": "（我看着她认真的眼神，做出了决定。）", "branch": "help"},
	{"type": "talk", "talker": "我", "talk_content": "当然，我会帮你的。告诉我接下来该怎么做。", "branch": "help"},
	{"type": "goto", "file_path": "test_path_help", "branch": "help"},
	{"type": "talk", "talk_content": "（我犹豫了一下，也许她只是最近压力太大了。）", "branch": "doubt"},
	{"type": "talk", "talker": "我", "talk_content": "你先冷静一下……这可能只是误会。你最近是不是太累了？", "branch": "doubt"},
	{"type": "goto", "file_path": "test_path_doubt", "branch": "doubt"},
	{"type": "talk", "talk_content": "（我什么也没说，转身推开了咖啡店的门。雨打在我的脸上。）", "branch": "leave"},
	{"type": "talk", "talker": "我", "talk_content": "对不起，我不该来的。", "branch": "leave", "wait": "2"},
	{"type": "goto", "file_path": "test_path_leave", "branch": "leave"}
  ]
}
